Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 前奏
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.36,0:00:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}提筆逐漸變困難\NIt's getting hard to write
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}時間也已這麼晚\Nand late into the night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}有好一陣子了，我還在往地上扔信\NIt's been while now, I toss the mail around
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}希望你最近過得好\NI hope you've been alright
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我仍急迫想知道\NI'm eager just to know
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}從此我該往何方\Nwhere, from this point, I go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.76,0:00:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我想你也知道，交朋友我都有做到\N'Cause I can tell you now, I've made my way around
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:01:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}但我似乎未曾成長\Nbut I never seem to grow
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.11,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}若你能看懂這封信件\NIf you can see right through this letter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}想必眼淚也會流滿面\Nthen all the tears are clearly shown
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}我想就這樣也許更好\NI guess it must be for the better
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}但我希望能讓你知道\Nbut I just thought I'd let you know
